11. Height and Width

width вҖ” controls horizontal size of element
height вҖ” controls vertical size of element
Values: px, %, vw, vh, auto
max-width вҖ” element will not grow beyond this value
min-width вҖ” element will not shrink below this value
max-height and min-height work the same way
Example:

css.card {
  width: 300px;
  height: 200px;
  max-width: 100%;
}

Rule: always set max-width: 100% on images to prevent overflow


12. Border

border shorthand: border: width style color
Example: border: 2px solid black
Border styles: solid, dashed, dotted, double, none
border-radius вҖ” rounds the corners of the border
Example:

css.box {
  border: 2px solid #333;
  border-radius: 8px;
}

13. Sides вҖ” Padding, Margin, Border Sides

All four sides can be set individually or with shorthand
Shorthand order: top, right, bottom, left (clockwise)

css/* All four sides same */
padding: 20px;

/* Top-bottom | Left-right */
padding: 10px 20px;

/* Top | Left-right | Bottom */
padding: 10px 20px 30px;

/* Top | Right | Bottom | Left */
padding: 10px 20px 30px 40px;

Individual sides:

padding-top, padding-right, padding-bottom, padding-left
margin-top, margin-right, margin-bottom, margin-left
border-top, border-right, border-bottom, border-left




Specificity вҖ” Which Style Wins?
SelectorSpecificityInline styleHighestID #idHighClass .classMediumElement pLow

When two rules conflict the one with higher specificity wins
When specificity is equal the one written later in the file wins


Mistakes I Made Today

Used ID selector for multiple elements вҖ” IDs must be unique
Confused descendant and child selector вҖ” descendant targets all levels, child targets one
Forgot shorthand order for padding вҖ” always clockwise: top right bottom left
Set height on a container вҖ” content overflowed when text increased

How I Fixed Them

Rule: class for reusable styles, ID only for truly unique elements
Rule: space between selectors = descendant, > between = direct child only
Rule: remember TRBL вҖ” Top Right Bottom Left for shorthand
Rule: avoid fixed heights on containers вҖ” let content determine height naturally

